  "instructions": [
    "Remove shrimp shells and devein, pat dry.",
    "In a bowl, combine olive oil, minced garlic, lime juice, smoked paprika, sea salt, and black pepper.",
    "Toss shrimp in the seasoning mixture until evenly coated.",
    "Prepare the glaze by crushing 30g Christmas pudding with soy sauce and parsley until smooth.",
    "Let shrimp marinate for 10 minutes.",
    "Preheat the binchotan grill to medium-high until glowing embers form.",
    "Place shrimp on the grill and cook for 2-3 minutes per side until pink and opaque.",
    "During the last minute of grilling, brush shrimp with glaze.",
    "Remove from grill, sprinkle with fresh parsley, and serve immediately."
